2011-10-07T20:57:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/blackrock-calls-for-tougher-regulation-of-etfs-audio-.html
 BlackRock Inc., the world's biggest
provider of exchange-traded funds, is calling for higher 
standards of disclosure and stronger, more uniform regulation of
the funds, according to the Business Times Singapore. Bloomberg 
Radio's Catherine Cowdery reports on Exchange Traded Funds.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:33
 